product.name: Hampton Bay Low-Voltage LED Black Bollard Light
product.description: Add style and enhance the beauty of your home and landscape with this professional-quality cast aluminum low-voltage LED bollard to illuminate pathways and low-lying greenery. The elegant fixture is reminiscent of something you might see along a wharf or dock, so it’s perfect for any dwelling near the waterfront or any residence whose owners have a nautical affinity. A frosted glass lens softens light output for an elegant look.
product.bullet_points:
• Features a cast aluminum bollard with black-finished body Emits a cool white light for charming nighttime luminescence Integrated LED lasts up to 50,000 hours
• Energy-efficient low-voltage LED consumes minimal electricity, costing just pennies per night to operate Cast aluminum construction, frosted glass and metal spike for rugged durability, stylish appearance and ease of installation
• Includes 12 in. SPT-1 18-Gauge cable and easy-to-use quick-clip connector Power pack and low-voltage cable sold separately
• Cool white integrated LED
